    <machine-print-line text="&quot;Good-bye, Dai,&quot; said Morfydd, smiling from the bottom step. &quot;Good-bye, Morfydd.&quot;" />
    <machine-print-line text="He sought to enfold her in his arms. But he was too late. She was already up the" />
    <machine-print-line text="bus steps, and the bus was away. And Morfydd Owen waving, unkissed, from the" />
    <machine-print-line text="window. And Dai, on the pavement, knowing in his heart that Morfydd was leaving" />
    <machine-print-line text="him as surely as she was leaving Dinas." />
  </machine-printed-part>
